Package net.netnook.repeg

Top level package for repeg library.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Context
    Context used by OnSuccessHandler to process matched input.
    Expression
    Common interface for expressions.
    ExpressionBuilder
    Common interface for all expression builders.
    OnSuccessHandler
    An OnSuccessHandler is the primary way to handle and process matched input in order to create a parse result.
    ParseListener
    Listener for parser events
    Parser<T>
    Parser interface.
    RuleEnum
    Specialised ExpressionBuilder used for defining expression builders using enums.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ParserFactoryBase<T>
    Base class for defining parsers.
